Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:24:34.17,WM,,0,0,0,,masssterchief
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:13.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:16.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.89,0:00:26.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:29.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Saru-chan, about the audition for the next Manten Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:39.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You see it too, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:41.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can see it too, Saru?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:42.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.94,0:00:43.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Kijimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:49.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There might be a {\i1}Zashiki-warashi{\i0} in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:54.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,They say that it brings good fortune, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:55.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good luck and...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:00.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Can you see it too, Kijimura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:04.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm looking at it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:12.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:15.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I told you to wait over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:20.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:26.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Your younger brother? \N-Your neighbor's child?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:28.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Your nephew? \N-Your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:29.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My sister's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:31.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's your sister's son, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:32.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.76,0:02:36.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My sister's husband got admitted into the hospital, so he was entrusted to me this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:38.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He had nowhere to go, so he ended up at Department 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:40.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He looks like a smart {\i1}Zashihki-warashi{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:42.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:42.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:43.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:44.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm 8 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:45.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,8 years old. Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:46.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Great?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:50.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because his daughter ignores him, just by talking to him makes him happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:53.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay Shoma, I'm going to take you to a good place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:55.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's a red light, Komukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:58.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,An alpha generation kid can't handle the Chief's passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:00.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:03.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A place where we can be the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:08.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you think Shoma?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:11.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My Lightning Avante Jr. is cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:12.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to build one for you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:15.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is he your son, Inuzuka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:19.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, he's Komukai's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:20.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You have a son?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, he's my nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:24.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:27.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to lend you mine, would you like to race with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:28.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:29.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:30.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel bad if you lend him your mini 4WD.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:31.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:34.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where is Big Stone Victory Magnum?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:36.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You call it by it's full name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:39.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're the one who named it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:42.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nakano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:45.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing in the middle of the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:48.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My boy Shoma and I are just feeling the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:49.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is he your nephew, Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:50.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:53.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course you're having fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:03.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:10.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Aren't you having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:16.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's too much, just do one line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:19.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that Nakano has that skill in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:23.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,According to the data, she is the oldest out of the three siblings, so her babysitting skills is at a pro level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:24.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good bye my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:26.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's going to be in your care for a while right? Are you going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:33.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's the first time that it's just the two of us, so I'm super worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:37.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shoma, take good care of Riko, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:38.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:40.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:05.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I took this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:07.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's already 3 years ago, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:16.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Both the 5 year old and 8 year old Shoma are so precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:18.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:20.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, did I interrupt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:23.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You came into my field of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:27.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Youtube.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:28.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What video?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:30.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Anijyaotojya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A Kabuki actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Gaming youtuber.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:35.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you play with your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:36.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Who is your best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:40.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,El-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:42.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is he a foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:45.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,An online game friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:48.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Online game friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is your favorite food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:55.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hi-Chew, the grape flavor is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:56.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you remember that I was the one who told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:05:58.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:02.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You used to say "Please marry me Riko" while eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:03.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:05.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,More importantly, what is Nakano-san like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:06.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:07.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're changing your favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:09.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She's so cool, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:13.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:17.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:21.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Five rules to become a mother from your big sister.]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:28.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[First, let him work on his homework on his own.]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:41.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alexa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:44.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,35 x 6 is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,210.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:46.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:48.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can't do that, solve it on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alexa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:54.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,27 x 53 is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:56.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,1431.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:03.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Second, have dinner at 7 PM.]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:07.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why are you cooking? You should just order from Uber Eats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:09.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's Curry Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:10.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:12.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? You like it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:15.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I prefer green curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:32.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Third, only 3 hours max of tablet use.]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's been more than 3 hours, Shoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:37.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:38.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Your mother will scold me if she finds out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:41.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She won't find out if you don't tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:42.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Fourth, make him call his mother (me).]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,-I did it all on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't use Alexa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:07:58.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko was with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:02.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sleep at 9, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Tablet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't use it all day, not even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Fifth, make him sleep at 9 PM.]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:18.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's already past 9 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:20.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's time to go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:23.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait, Otojya-san is streaming right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You promised your mother that you're going to bed early.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:27.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Lying leads to stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:32.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:34.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:49.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:51.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:53.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Your hair is so messy, Zakunee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:56.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you have a plastic model that kids can have fun with?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Plastic model is open to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:00.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There is no age barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:02.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There is an age target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How old is the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:06.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's an 8 year old boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:20.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,SD Gundam BB Warrior LEGEND BB Musha Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:24.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a series of deformed versions of mobile suits from the Gundam series.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:26.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Deformed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:27.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:33.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The name "BB Warrior" comes from the gimmick of firing BB bullets mounted on the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:37.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The new version of that legendary series is called LEGEND BB Series.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It looks so cute and fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:46.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is the Gundam that in the turbulent times, as the leader of the Seven Warriors, fought many battles against the Dark Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:48.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's going to strike you down if you underestimate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:50.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:58.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Have you seen my tablet, Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:00.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I've hid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:01.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,WHY?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:08.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:11.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's super basic to hide it under the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:23.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It was super easy to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:24.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you a child, Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:40.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find it anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:41.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is what happens when adults get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:43.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:48.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,For you, Shoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:49.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:50.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Where is my tablet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:53.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is a BB Gundam plastic model.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:54.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's build this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:55.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Give my tablet back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:11:00.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Look, it looks cute but it's actually really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:01.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:06.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did I told you that I like those kind of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:09.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,About the curry and Hi-Chew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:15.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,When did that happen again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:17.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Just the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:19.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,3 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:23.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not the same person as I was back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:07.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making assumptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:12.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I haven't changed a bit in this past three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:15.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,so I treated you just like I did back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:18.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But your three years is completely different, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:20.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Three years is a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:27.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,When you became an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:30.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,time flies so fast looking at the same thing all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It makes me a bit sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:39.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's the one that I bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The grape flavor is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:51.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We've now made up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:53.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you an {\i1}ikemen{\i0} or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:55.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:57.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:01.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How do you build this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:05.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you want to build it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:06.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:13.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:12.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:20.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:23.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's something even more amazing over there, Shoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:24.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't say another word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:29.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's the eyes of someone who is shaking with amazement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:31.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:35.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Can I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can do anything with plastic models.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:38.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:43.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,As you assemble the parts, it's so exciting that I'm going to have a nose bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:43.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:44.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:51.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Open the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:52.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:53.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't mind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:56.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This time, there are a lot of weapons and other things with sharp tips,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:58.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,so be careful and go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:06.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is this a Yari?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:08.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is called Naginata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:18.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Tanegashima Rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:23.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a sword, Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:25.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's the famous sword, Bukyumaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:26.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're even more amazing than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:29.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yassan even loves the name of the weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:30.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:36.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.84,0:15:37.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:49.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're so good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:56.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I just have to build it according to this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:07.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you want to create your own Musha Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:11.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You have to paint it if you want it to look like the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:13.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The most important thing is undercoating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:14.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's completely different from the instruction manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The paint battle is still ongoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:46.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Next up is the topcoat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:49.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is your favorite color, Shoma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:51.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:54.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's like a Musha Gundam that fell into the darkness, it gives me goosebumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:56.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Fell into the darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:00.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If you want it to look cool, imagine it in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why black?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:04.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why did it fell into the darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:09.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Someone betrayed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:13.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,By a friend whom it once fought with?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:14.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,More.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:16.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You have to be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:19.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm having quite the hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:27.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If the one who betrayed Musha Gundam is it's own brother, it's going to be even sadder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:32.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Go for it, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:33.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:35.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:54.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:00.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:02.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What a good darkness this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:18.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There are two heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Once you assemble it, you can also make it to be a foot soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:28.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Foot soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:31.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Infantrymen that are at the front of the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:35.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The simplicity of the design expresses the fleetingness and melancholy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:38.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I prefer Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:42.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can do anything with plastic models.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:53.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:56.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You say "Give birth" once you have completed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:57.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:02.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Gundam marker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:04.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The battle is not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:05.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Young man,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:07.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,if you want to make it look the coolest,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:09.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,break trough the ceiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:32.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Inking the {\i1}Kabuto{\i0} gives it a more three-dimensional and realistic feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:37.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So detailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,All that remains is putting on it's weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Young man, take up arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:54.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's time to go to battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:02.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:06.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Musha Gundam, give birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:08.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's so cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:54.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The future of the children is the future of plastic models.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:56.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Likewise, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:20:59.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I got a lot of notifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:02.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's going viral.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:06.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You posted this online?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:08.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:10.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:13.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:15.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:19.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:21.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:23.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:24.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:26.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:29.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,8 year olds these days are peerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:32.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because there is no target age for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:34.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:36.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:39.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You like that Oishi person, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:43.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:45.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're my aunt and my ex-fiancee.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:47.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It was easy to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:50.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I like Oishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:52.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:56.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You have the same look when looking at plastic model and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:21:58.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,And also, you act weird around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:02.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't assume things about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:03.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:04.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:05.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We work at the same company.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.56,0:22:07.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm also in the same class as my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:08.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.56,0:22:12.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Adults do over think things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:18.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:20.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:21.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:23.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A charm for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:25.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:26.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,muster up the courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:28.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,and take arms to Oishi, the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.32,0:22:30.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:31.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:32.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.80,0:22:34.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Absolutely you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:37.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.55,0:22:39.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:41.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,